data.description: Investor special!!! Investors won't go wrong with this duplex in the increasingly high demand community of Marion Village area.  This large duplex is located west of Parsons.  Both units offer new HVAC units, new H2O tanks, and new electric installed.  Exterior offers new vinyl siding.  Some drywall needs to be finished and some new windows will need replaced.  Investor to finish from drywall onto completion. Good cash flow once completed!  Cash buyer only - As is home!  Buyer will not be able to obtain financing.
